summary: THE VEHICLE WOULD NOT START; ENGINE CRANKS W/O STARTING.  INITIALLY IT WOULD CRANK FOR LONG PERIODS, IE. 20 SECONDS, AND START.  THEN NOT AT ALL. TOOK IT TO DEALER, WHO WAS AWARE OF SERVICE BULLETIN ISSUED RE: FUEL DELIVERY SYSTEM, AT TANK FUEL PUMP PROBLEM.  REPAIR WAS MADE AT COST OF APPR. $400.00.  I FEEL THIS SHOULD BE A RECALL AND REPAIR SHOULD HAVE BEEN MADE FREE OF CHARGE.
